SELECT VALOR FROM <?=odiRef.getSchemaName() ?>.TBL_GAI_PARAMETROS T1 WHERE 1=1 AND T1.PARAMETRO = 'V_NOMBR_JAR_CORREO' AND T1.COD_PADRE = 0 AND ROWNUM = 1
